*******************************************************
PER TROVARE GLI ERRORI, CERCARE LA STRINGA #ERRORE#
PER TROVARE I WARNING, CERCARE LA STRINGA #WARNING#
PER TROVARE I DUPLICATI, CERCARE LA STRINGA #DUPLICATO#
*******************************************************

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.1.0\fix\V5R2M0/46872/tddml/SGQ_MISURE_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.SGQ_MISURE_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.SGQ_MISURE_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.SGQ_MISURE_V01 AS SELECT  MIS.* ,  MISCAR .SEQ_VISUALIZZ  FROM THIP.SGQ_MISURE MIS
           LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.SGQ_MIS_CAR  MISCAR ON 
			   MIS.ID_AZIENDA = MISCAR.ID_AZIENDA  AND
			   MIS.ID_TIPO_DOC_PRV = MISCAR.ID_TIPO_DOC_PRV AND
			   MIS.ID_ANNO_DOC =  MISCAR.ID_ANNO_DOC AND
			   MIS.ID_NUMERO_DOC = MISCAR.ID_NUMERO_DOC AND
			   MIS.ID_RIGA_DOC = MISCAR.ID_RIGA_DOC AND
			   MIS.ID_NUMERO_ISTANZA = MISCAR.ID_NUMERO_ISTANZA AND
			   MIS.ID_SEQUENZA_FASE = MISCAR.ID_SEQUENZA_FASE AND
			   MIS.ID_SEQUENZA_CAR = MISCAR.ID_SEQUENZA_CAR

CREATE TABLE THIP.GWMSO00F_CLIENTI
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   FONTE_ORIGINE CHAR(10) NOT NULL,
   STATO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'V',
   R_SERIE CHAR(2),
   R_NUMERATORE CHAR(15),
   RIASSEGNA_PREZZI CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   STATO_ORD CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'D',
   ELIMINA_RECORD CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   COD_CAU_VEN_TES CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   DEFAULT_CAU_VEN CHAR(1),
   ID_COMMENT_USE CHAR(15),
   COD_CAU_VEN_RIG CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   DEFAULT_CAU_RIG CHAR(1),
   STAMPA_CONF_ORD CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   CREA_OMAGGI CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   IMP_CLI_CONT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   ID_CLIENTE CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
CONSTRAINT GWMCLI2GWMSO FOREIGN KEY (ID_AZIENDA, FONTE_ORIGINE)
        REFERENCES THIP.GWMSO00F
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX GWMSOCLI_PK ON THIP.GWMSO00F_CLIENTI (ID_AZIENDA ASC, FONTE_ORIGINE ASC, ID_CLIENTE ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.GWMSO00F_CLIENTI ADD PRIMARY KEY  (ID_AZIENDA, FONTE_ORIGINE, ID_CLIENTE)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.GWMSO00F_CLIENTI TO PUBLIC

CREATE TABLE THIP.PSN_CATALOGO_TEMP
(
   ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   MAIL_TO VARCHAR(1000),
   DIR_BLAT VARCHAR(256),
   UTENTE_DOMINO VARCHAR(50),
   PWD_UTENTE_DOMINO VARCHAR(50),
   TIMESTAMP DATETIME,
   ANYWAY_MAIL CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y'
)  ON 'THIP4'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.1.0\fix\V5R2M0/47665/primrose/script/01Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCMOVV54 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCMOVV54 (
    T01CD,
    T09CD,
    MOVNUREG,
    MOVNRIRE,
    MOVSTATO,
    T04CD,
    VOCCD,
    MOVTPVAL,
    MOVTCLFO,
    CLICD,
    FORCD,
    MOVDTRCO,
    MOVDTCOM,
    MOVDTDOC,
    MOVDTVAL,
    MOVAAPAR,
    MOVNPIVA,
    MOVNDORI,
    MOVNRPAR,
    MOVNUPRA,
    MOVSEGNO,
    MOVIMPVP,
    MOVIMPVS,
    T29CD,
    MOVIMPVE,
    MOVCAMBVP,
    MOVCAMBVS,
    T02CD,
    MOVTICAU,
    MOVDSCAU,
    MOVDSAGG,
    MOVIVA,
    T05CD,
    MOVTCFCO,
    MOVCLICO,
    MOVCLIRC,
    MOVVOCCC,
    VOCCTPDS,
    FORCNTRP,
    MOVFORRD,
    MOVCOMUL,
    T36CD,
    MOVINUSO,
    MOVTPMOV
) AS

SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T09CD,
    T1.MOVNUREG,
    T1.MOVNRIRE,
    T1.MOVSTATO,
    T1.T04CD,
    T1.VOCCD,
    T1.MOVTPVAL,
    T1.MOVTCLFO,
    T1.CLICD,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOVDTCOM,
    T1.MOVDTDOC,
    T1.MOVDTVAL,
    T1.MOVAAPAR,
    T1.MOVNPIVA,
    T1.MOVNDORI,
    T1.MOVNRPAR,
    T1.MOVNUPRA,
    T1.MOVSEGNO,
    T1.MOVIMPVP,
    T1.MOVIMPVS,
    T1.T29CD,
    T1.MOVIMPVE,
    T1.MOVCAMBVP,
    T1.MOVCAMBVS,
    T1.T02CD,
    T1.MOVTICAU,
    T1.MOVDSCAU,
    T1.MOVDSAGG,
    T1.MOVIVA,
    T1.T05CD,
    T1.MOVTCFCO,
    T1.MOVCLICO,
    T2.CLIRASOC,
    T1.MOVVOCCC,
    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T1.FORCNTRP,
    T4.FORRASOC,
    T1.MOVCOMUL,
    T1.T36CD,
    T1.MOVINUSO,
    T1.MOVTPMOV
FROM
      FINANCE.BCMOVPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBFORPT T4
     ON  T1.T01CD = T4.T01CD AND
         T1.FORCNTRP = T4.FORCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.MOVVOCCC = T3.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBCLIPT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.MOVCLICO = T2.CLICD
    

E' stata applicata la fix 47665
